divs: Sighting DetailsI was watching sky and this object flew forward and then backward. As it moved backward I took a photo and it was lighting 3 bulbs under itself. Suddenly it became brighter, when I took a photo I could see 6 light bulbs under it. I was chasing it in my car, I drove to where it headed backward and I couldn't see it. I decided to go back home, which is the forward direction of that object and I found it agin flying foward. I followed it and the object stopped and lighted just one light, blinking and it looked just like a star, a blinking star. I watched it for 5 minutes and it didnot move so I thought it might be a star, and then it suddenly turned on the light bulbs again and moved to north east, I think.
Summary: 6 light bulbs under it, moving forward an backward, stationary, and moving again.
